OL,3,CWill pension reforms 'unlock billions
OL,4,Cto drive growth'?
OL,6,FSurplus money could be deployed for
OL,7,Fgrowth-rich investment. Less usefully,
OL,8,Fit could be used to help fund dividend
OL,9,Fpayments or share buybacks.
OL,11,FAnd pension trustees, who oversee and
OL,12,Fmanage DB schemes to ensure they
OL,13,Fdeliver the promised benefits for
OL,14,Fmembers, have a duty to be cautious.
OL,16,FThe steep rise in interest rates since
OL,17,F2021 has helped to propel many DB
OL,18,Fschemes from deficit to surplus, but
OL,19,Frates can go down as well as up.
