OL,3,CWill pension reforms 'unlock billions
OL,4,Cto drive growth'?
OL,6,FAnd if a company ends up bust and
OL,7,Funable to make good on the future
OL,8,Fpromises it has made, then the Pension
OL,9,FProtection Fund will only cover 90% of
OL,10,Ffuture benefits for the not-yet
OL,11,Fretired - as members of the BHS and
OL,12,FCarillion schemes found out.
OL,14,FThe government may be feeling bullish
OL,15,Fand intrepid but trustees are likely
OL,16,Fto be more hesitant, vetoing ideas
OL,17,Fthey don't like.
OL,19,FChanging the rules may not "unlock"
OL,20,Fanything like #160 billion for
OL,21,Finvestment, we just don't know.
